  "text": "On the other hand, multiple manufacturing constraints should be considered in a design process. From the engineering perspective, the ply drops in tapered composite structures should be avoided or as few as possible to decrease stress concentration and improve structural integrity. A detailed design guidelines are introduced in [CITATION_1] . The objective function for optimization is formulated as follows: CT10:Ply -drop alternation: Ply drops should be located alternately close and far from the mid plane:",
